{"tid":36840,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【多謝幫忙】Arc2HKG beta 1.2 已出","createTime":"2016-12-13T03:27:14.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T14:55:45.000Z","uid":11598,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f403b2550f9e188817f61ea7fc2867fd5d9d33c0","tid":36840,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T03:27:14.000Z","msg":"V1.2 :<br />\n+ 主題列表長按功能選單<br />\n+ 選單轉頁<br />\n+ 讀Post 嵌入式 Youtube Player<br />\n+ Limoji 擴充表情圖示系統框架<br />\n+ 加入 Lomoji<br />\n+ new bugs 🐍<br />\n[Fix] 讀Post Memory Leak問題<br />\n[Fix] 主題列表錯位<br />\n[Fix] 數個會導致彈App 潛在問題<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好嘢 終於有更新,不過仲未有登入,回覆,回帶<br />\n不過功能上未能夠Daily use  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢排有啲忙，所以進度龜速，sor9 sor9  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好感激啲巴絲打連日來不斷玩爛個App，係咁FC，我係咁收Email話Fatal <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，亦都係因為佢哋而Fix咗好多bugs<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然係咁，都拜託An機嘅大家幫幫手試下<br />\n我哋需要用戶feedback先可以做得更好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n先按成為測試人員 <a href=\"https://play.google.com/apps/testing/com.bus.arc2hkg \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fapps%2Ftesting%2Fcom.bus.arc2hkg%20&d=T5GqAMoknpQKFzmuFUSIu0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=b81ed837\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/apps/testing/com.bus.arc2hkg </a><br />\n再往<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.bus.arc2hkg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.bus.arc2hkg&d=T5GqAMoknpQKFzmuFUSIu0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=93799367\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.bus.arc2hkg</a><br />\n下載<br />\n<br />\n如果鍾意個App嘅唔該幫幫手去Facebook page 比個like / feedback <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/archkgolden\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Farchkgolden&d=T5GqAMoknpQKFzmuFUSIu0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=379e2488\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/archkgolden</a><br />\n<br />\n除咗Facebook Page ，我哋都已經有Telegram 官方頻道啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即刻Subscribe 埋佢我哋緊貼最新update!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://telegram.me/arc2hkg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegram.me%2Farc2hkg&d=T5GqAMoknpQKFzmuFUSIu0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=493eab41\" target=\"_blank\">https://telegram.me/arc2hkg</a><br />\n<br />\n有Bug屎請隨便擺低 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有關要求賬戶權限，之前試驗性質想將Arc2HKG 登入嘅帳號嵌入Android 個Account<br />\n所以要Get Account 同 Auth Account 權，本程式絕對唔會讀你其他account資料（亦都拎唔到）<br />\n暫時已經諗到第二個方法處理呢啲敏感問題，期望之後會取代呢個方法<br />\n<br />\n有關作為 LiHKG 第三方應用程式許可事宜<br />\nArc2HKG 已經收到由 LiHKG 官方發言人發出的LIHKG API 使用條款<br />\n條款中已詳細列出各項我們認為可以接受的要求，故此我們接受 LiHKG API 使用條款並正式成為 LiHKG 第三方應用程式<br />\n由於條款中列出需要放置官方廣告以支援 LiHKG 官方的營運資金，Arc2HKG 將會於稍後進行相關作業。<br />\n由於暫時未能尋求以IAP去除廣告方案，Arc2HKG將等候LiHKG 官方說明相關條款再作修正與增補，多謝各位支持Arc2HKG。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7